title: KR3W KLIPS: LAS VEGAS
description:
LAS V3GAS, the city of all things gone wrong, is the backdrop for this first KR3W KLIPS installment. Kevin Romar, Boo Johnson, Dane Vaughn, Windsor James, Lizard King, and Erik Ellington all hustled out to the city of sin on President's Day weekend for a Pharmacy signing and enjoyed a little extra-curricular shredding around town with local KR3W flow rider Phillip "Pip" Meranto. Please enjoy these KLIPS from the KR3W.

SITE: http://kr3wdenim.com/
